# Dr. Martin Luther King Jr. Expressway

Dr. Martin Luther King Jr. Expressway may refer to:
*Martin Luther King Jr. Expressway (Portsmouth)
*New York State Route 440
*Interstate 65 in Kentucky
*Interstate 110 (Louisiana)
*Interstate 244
